<li>Lupo, Salvatore (2009), <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=Winf_4mif90C">The History of the Mafia</a></i>, New York: Columbia University Press, <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/><a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-231-13134-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-231-13134-6">978-0-231-13134-6</a></li>
<li><span style="padding: 0; font-size: x-small; font-weight: bold; color: #000000; background-color: #f9f9f9;" class="tfd"><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Templates_for_discussion/Log/2019_June_9#Link_language_wrappers" title="Wikipedia:Templates for discussion/Log/2019 June 9">‹See Tfd›</a></span><span class="languageicon">(in Italian)</span> <a href="/wiki/Gaetano_Mosca" title="Gaetano Mosca">Mosca, Gaetano</a> (1901/2015). <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=TsMYBwAAQBAJ">Che cosa è la mafia?</a></i>, Messina: Il Grano, <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/><a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-88-99045-11-1" title="Special:BookSources/978-88-99045-11-1">978-88-99045-11-1</a> (See <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.liberliber.it/mediateca/libri/m/mosca/che_cosa_e_la_mafia/pdf/mosca_che_cosa_e_la_mafia.pdf">Full text in Italian</a> and the <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=NzNhBAAAQBAJ">English translation</a> for a background on the publication)</li>
<li>Mosca, Gaetano (1901/2014). <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=NzNhBAAAQBAJ">"What is Mafia"</a></i>, M&amp;J, 2014. Translation of the book "Che cosa è la Mafia", Giornale degli Economisti, July 1901, pp.&#160;236–62. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/><a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/979-11-85666-00-6" title="Special:BookSources/979-11-85666-00-6">979-11-85666-00-6</a></li>
<li>Paoli, Letizia (2003). <i>Mafia Brotherhoods: Organized Crime, Italian Style</i>. Oxford/New York: Oxford University Press. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/><a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-19-515724-9" title="Special:BookSources/0-19-515724-9">0-19-515724-9</a></li>
<li>Seindal, René (1998). <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=kJf-oKqos1YC">Mafia: Money and Politics in Sicily, 1950-1997</a></i>. Copenhagen: Museum Tusculanum Press. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/><a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/87-7289-455-5" title="Special:BookSources/87-7289-455-5">87-7289-455-5</a></li>
<li>Servadio, Gaia (1976). <i>Mafioso: a history of the Mafia from its origins to the present day</i>. London: Secker &amp; Warburg. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/><a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-436-44700-2" title="Special:BookSources/0-436-44700-2">0-436-44700-2</a></li>
<li>Wang, Peng (2017). <i>The Chinese Mafia: Organized Crime, Corruption, and Extra-Legal Protection</i>. Oxford: Oxford University Press. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/><a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780198758402" title="Special:BookSources/9780198758402">9780198758402</a></li></ul>
